			<h1 class="page-title">BA in the Teaching of English</h1>



<div id="textcontainer" class="page_content">

<div class="sidebar">
	<div id="sidebar-contact">








<p class="program_codes"><span class="label"><strong>Program Codes:</strong> </span><br />20FT0288BA<br /></p>	</div>
</div>

<h2>Degree Requirements</h2>
<p>To earn a Bachelor of Arts in the Teaching of English degree from UIC, students must complete university, college, and department degree requirements. The Department of English degree requirements are outlined below. Students should consult the <a href="/ucat/colleges-depts/liberal-arts-sciences/"><em>College of Liberal Arts and Sciences</em></a> section for additional degree requirements and college academic policies.</p>
